# AGOF vault overlay for RamenDR TechDemo (OpenShift / hub Vault)
#
# On OpenShift with doAutoHubVaultConfig enabled, leave this file empty.
# AAP credentials are sourced from hub Vault via controller_credential_input_sources
# in controller_config.yml. Populate secrets with:
#   ./pattern.sh make load-secrets
#
# See values-secret.yaml.template for required secret names and fields.
---
# Intentionally empty — secrets live in hub Vault, not in agof-vault-file.
